---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Waterfalls | Fine Art Waterfall Photography | Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
description: "Fine art waterfall photography by Fabrizio Vinciguerra, exploring the quiet relationship between flowing water, light, movement and time through long exposure landscapes."
ogImage: "https://www.fabriziovinciguerraph.com/assets/images/social/og-image.jpg"
ogImageAlt: "Fine art waterfall photography by Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
---

<section class="collection-hero">

  <img
    src="/assets/images/waterfalls.jpg"
    alt="Fine art waterfall landscape photographed by Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
  >

  <div class="collection-hero-content">
    <p class="subtitle">Collection 02</p>

    <h1>Waterfalls</h1>

    <p>
      Where movement meets stillness.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>

<section class="fine-art-story waterfall-story">

  {% for photo in waterfalls %}

    {% if loop.index == 1 %}

      <figure class="story-image travel-image {{ photo.class }} reveal">

        <img
          src="{{ photo.src }}"
          alt="{{ photo.alt }}"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="lightbox-image"
          data-full="{{ photo.src }}"
          data-title=""
        >

      </figure>

      <div class="travel-quote reveal">
        <p>
          Water is never still.<br>
          It shapes stone, carries light and quietly rewrites the landscape.
        </p>
      </div>

    {% else %}

      {% if loop.index == 6 %}

        <div class="travel-quote reveal">
          <p>
            Every waterfall is different.<br>
            Yet they all speak the same language.
          </p>
        </div>

      {% endif %}

      <figure class="story-image travel-image {{ photo.class }} reveal">

        <img
          src="{{ photo.src }}"
          alt="{{ photo.alt }}"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="lightbox-image"
          data-full="{{ photo.src }}"
          data-title=""
        >

      </figure>

    {% endif %}

  {% endfor %}

  <div class="travel-closing reveal">
    <p>
      Long after the sound has faded,<br>
      the landscape continues to speak.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>